<img class="img-responsive mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-md" src="screens/5.3-06-en.png">
    <ul>
      <li>leave <strong>Let  MaxBack decide</strong> the selection to the question <strong>Do you wish to split eligible pension  income with your spouse?</strong></li>
